channel.title: Score (Esturgy Remix) - INFEKT [Riddim/Dubstep]
channel.description:
Hi, it's Esturgy again. Here is a remix I made for Disciple's Biggest Remix Competition of All Time.
https://soundcloud.com/lord-sturge/infekt-score-esturgy-remix
Auxy drums were used for this song along with some samples I exported. Please be sure to leave a like or any constructive comments if you want to!
Also be sure to go stream the original song by Infekt.
